{"tid":2067575,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"1999年《黑社會檔案之黑金帝國》揭露中共鄉黑聯手犯罪電影","createTime":"2020-06-17T05:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T06:02:28.000Z","uid":129019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c8426211ccfcbb7a2aee16a5a6351bd1086b4e94","tid":2067575,"uid":129019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:46:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Vn7QrWq4Rno\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVn7QrWq4Rno&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG28KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=27279adc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Vn7QrWq4Rno</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hn74qYj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHn74qYj.jpg&h=ad18c91c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b79426cd47b2ac44e6d368b2cc27829e49d1e6e","tid":2067575,"uid":129019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iobs8fi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiobs8fi.jpg&h=66e68ccd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑社會檔案之黑金帝國<br />\n主演：黃秋生、 陳惠敏、彭丹、午馬、胡渭康<br />\n<br />\n新界某鄉市黑社會執委員會主席何權，獲悉特區政府準建設西鐵發展計劃事宜，確定沿線發展區域一帶，大量撥地興建丁屋，串謀某一派鄉事執委週甘銓、羅偉雄、梁召權、趙振明等人，進行非法行賄認定原居民，以厚利報酬而換取支持投票當選為主席，以便日後進身立法機關執法，好待以主席身份代表鄉民向特區政府商議土地收購索償。廉署高層幹部接獲此案，據案情涉及西鐵發展計劃，牽涉人仕甚廣，隨即成立項目小組調查此案，並設立代號為「西域黑金」行動。"},{"pid":"b2986b8d29349d8eb5e975eb9c0da2ec0e48dc71","tid":2067575,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T06:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}